movie.title: The Devil Has a Name
movie.description_intro: A psychotic oil matriarch leaves the whole industry exposed when she attempts to outfight a bullish farmer whose water has been poisoned.
movie.description_full: A psychotic oil matriarch leaves the whole industry exposed when she attempts to outfight a bullish farmer whose water has been poisoned.

movies.title: Bad Hombres
movies.summary: Meet the Tecolotes, the world's only binational professional baseball team whose home games are played in Laredo, TX and Nuevo Laredo, Mexico. With US-Mexico relations reaching an historic low point, the team's cross-border heritage serves as a powerful symbol of unity. Follow as their season unfolds, revealing what life is like in a border city besieged by divisive rhetoric and policies, all in the shadow of America's favorite pastime.

movies.title: Popstar: Never Stop Never Stopping
movies.summary: When his new album fails to sell records, pop and rap superstar conner4real (Andy Samberg) goes into a major tailspin and watches his celebrity high life begin to collapse. He'll try anything to bounce back, anything except reuniting with his old rap group The Style Boyz.

movies.title: Family Members
movies.summary: Body-obsessed teenager Lucas and his mystically-inclined older sister, Gilda, unexpectedly become stranded when they travel to a nearly deserted coastal town to try to fulfill their dead mother's last wishes in whatever way they can.

movies.title: Betrayed
movies.summary: In an effort to control the city the Mayor opens the doors to the Russian Mob. It is not long until he realizes they aren't going to follow his rules. To fix the problem he accepts an offer to set up the Russians and open the door for the Cartel. When the Russians find out they take the Mayors Daughter and then the real games begin.
